                  <br/>
                  <paragraph>Glycopyrrolate Tablets USP, 2 mg are white, round tablets with debossing of “OL” above bisect and “318” below bisect on one side and plain on the other side.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>They are supplied as follows: </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 100 Tablets     (NDC 15955-318-01)<br/>
                     <br/>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Store at 20˚to 25˚C (68˚to 77˚F) [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].  </content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Dispense in a tight container as defined in the USP. <br/>
                        <br/>
